Summary of tt_test() results.

summary.tt_df.Rd

Summary of tt_test() results.

# S3 method for tt_df
summary(object, ...)

# S3 method for tt_lst
summary(object, ...)

Arguments

object

An object of a valid S3 class (see usage).
...

Other arguments passed to methods. * <tt_df>: Unused. * <tt_lst>: Unused.

Value

A tibble.

See also

tt_test(), base::summary().

Other methods for common generics: as_tibble.demography_ctfs, as_tibble.tt_lst

Examples

tt_result <- tt_test(fgeo.x::tree6_3species, fgeo.x::habitat)
#> Using `plotdim = c(320, 500)`. To change this value see `?tt_test()`.
#> Using `gridsize = 20`. To change this value see `?tt_test()`.

summary(tt_result)
#> # A tibble: 12 x 3
